name: Forme Physique
overview:
Forme Physique was formed to be the premier personal training provider. As one of the founders of Forme Physique, Jim knows what it is like to be one of “the clients”. After years of working with a personal trainer, Jim has achieved some amazing, life changing results and understands what a client wants and needs. Click here for Jim’s full story.

With this in mind, the concept of Forme Physique was born. We understand that our clients may need one, more, or all of the following features to help them achieve their desired results:

Weight Loss
Toning
Strength
Nutritional guidance
